#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_theme.rst:19
msgid ""
"A theme for skinning controls. Controls can be skinned individually, but "
"for complex applications, it's more practical to just create a global "
"theme that defines everything. This theme can be applied to any "
":ref:`Control <class_Control>`; the Control and its children will "
"automatically use it."
msgstr ""
"控件外观的主题。控件可以单独设置外观，但是对于复杂的应用程序，创建一个定义所有内容的全局主题更为实用。该主题可以应用于任何 "
":ref:`Control <class_Control>`；控件及其子级将自动使用它。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_theme.rst:21
msgid ""
"Theme resources can alternatively be loaded by writing them in a "
"``.theme`` file, see the documentation for more information."
msgstr "也可以通过将主题资源写入 ``.theme`` 文件中，来加载主题资源，有关更多信息，请参见文档。"

